cqueue
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% CQUEUE — syntax quick-ref
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% Header/items:
%%   cqueue                        (block form; directives below)
%%   cells <v1> <v2> …             (use _ · . · - for empty slots)
%%   items <v1> <v2> …             (alias for cells)
%% Options:  title <text> · capacity <N> · front <idx> · rear <idx>
%% Axis:     axis horizontal (default) · axis vertical
%% Anchors:  c0 · c1 · … cn  (ring cells, 0-based)
%% Demo:     vertical ring buffer with front/rear and wrap arc.
%% Comments: full-line %% text is stripped before parse; inline/trailing %% is not.
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  title vertical ring buffer
  capacity 6
  cells _ B C D _ F
  front 1
  rear 5
  axis vertical
